                    <h2>Implementation horror stories</h2>
                    <p>ERP implementation blunders are kind of a “thing” in the software world, and these failed implementations are getting more and more expensive.</p><a href="reinventing-erp.html" class="" ><button class="btn btn-warning">How we're fixing it</button></a>
